---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CTABand from '@/components/CTABand.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Estate Planning | Heidi Blondin Financial"
  description="Protect your legacy and ensure your wishes are followed. Wills, powers of attorney, beneficiary designations, and tax-efficient estate strategies from Heidi Blondin Financial."
>

  <section class="bg-brand-plum py-20">
    <div class="container-content max-w-3xl">
      <p class="eyebrow-light mb-5">Planning</p>
      <h1 class="font-serif text-display text-white text-balance" style="font-optical-sizing: auto;">Estate Planning</h1>
      <p class="font-sans text-[18px] text-white/65 mt-5 leading-relaxed">
        Estate planning isn't just for the wealthy — it's for anyone who cares about what happens to the people and things they love. We help you put the right structures in place, at every stage of life.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-white section-gap">
    <div class="container-content max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-h2 text-brand-plum mb-6" style="font-optical-sizing: auto;">What estate planning actually covers</h2>
      <div class="font-sans text-[17px] text-brand-ink/75 leading-relaxed space-y-4">
        <p>Most people think of estate planning as writing a will — and that's an important start. But a complete estate plan also addresses what happens if you become incapacitated, how your assets transfer to beneficiaries efficiently, and how to minimize the tax burden your estate leaves behind.</p>
        <p>Done well, estate planning gives you peace of mind now and gives your family clarity later — preventing conflict, delays, and unnecessary costs when they're already dealing with grief.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 space-y-5">
        <div class="bg-brand-tintPlum p-6">
          <h3 class="font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-brand-plum mb-2">Will and beneficiary review</h3>
          <p class="font-sans text-[14px] text-brand-ink/65 leading-relaxed">We review your beneficiary designations on registered accounts, life insurance, and pension plans — because these override your will. Out-of-date beneficiary designations are one of the most common estate planning mistakes, and one of the easiest to fix.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-brand-tintPlum p-6">
          <h3 class="font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-brand-plum mb-2">Powers of attorney</h3>
          <p class="font-sans text-[14px] text-brand-ink/65 leading-relaxed">A Power of Attorney for Property and a Power of Attorney for Personal Care give someone you trust the legal authority to make decisions on your behalf if you're unable to. Without these documents, your family may need a court order — an expensive and stressful process.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-brand-tintPlum p-6">
          <h3 class="font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-brand-plum mb-2">Tax-efficient asset transfer</h3>
          <p class="font-sans text-[14px] text-brand-ink/65 leading-relaxed">We help structure how assets pass — through beneficiary designations, joint ownership, trusts, or life insurance — to minimize probate fees and the deemed disposition taxes triggered at death. This can preserve significantly more of your estate for your heirs.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-brand-tintPlum p-6">
          <h3 class="font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-brand-plum mb-2">Life insurance in estate planning</h3>
          <p class="font-sans text-[14px] text-brand-ink/65 leading-relaxed">Life insurance can equalize inheritances among beneficiaries, provide liquidity to pay estate taxes without forcing asset sales, or leave a tax-free gift to charities or family members — often at a fraction of the policy's face value.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-brand-tintPlum p-6">
          <h3 class="font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-brand-plum mb-2">Charitable giving strategies</h3>
          <p class="font-sans text-[14px] text-brand-ink/65 leading-relaxed">If philanthropy is part of your legacy, we help structure donations that are tax-efficient — reducing the estate's tax burden while directing meaningful gifts to the causes you care about. <a href="/charitable-giving/" class="text-brand-gold hover:underline">Learn more about charitable giving →</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 bg-brand-tintSage p-6 border-l-2 border-brand-sage">
        <h3 class="font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-brand-plum mb-2">Free resources for estate planning</h3>
        <p class="font-sans text-[14px] text-brand-ink/70 leading-relaxed mb-3">Download our planning documents to help you prepare:</p>
        <a href="/resources/" class="font-sans text-[14px] text-brand-plum hover:text-brand-gold transition-colors flex items-center gap-1.5">
          <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5 21 12m0 0-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"/></svg>
          Legacy Planning Checklist, Will Planning Worksheet, Executor Checklist, and more
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10 bg-brand-tintPlum p-5 border-l-2 border-brand-plum/30">
        <p class="font-sans text-xs text-brand-ink/55 leading-relaxed">Insurance products are offered through Heidi Blondin Financial / Qualified Financial Services. This article is for general information purposes only and does not constitute personalized financial, legal, or tax advice. Estate planning often involves legal documents (wills, powers of attorney) that require a qualified estate lawyer. We work alongside your legal advisor as part of an integrated planning team.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTABand heading="Start the estate planning conversation" sub="Book a free consultation and we'll walk through what you have in place and what still needs attention." />

</BaseLayout>
